  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> are located on floors 1-6. These rooms are around 25-30m², and sleep two to three people. These rooms have an ensuite with bath (with overhead shower).</p>
<p><strong>Standard Queen Rooms</strong> are located on floors 1-6. These rooms are around 20m², sleep two people, and have an ensuite with shower. These rooms are available for single occupancy for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Single Rooms</strong> are around 19m² and on floors 1-6. They have an ensuite with shower. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Twin Rooms</strong> are located on floors 7-14. These rooms are around 25-30m², and sleep two to three people. These rooms have an ensuite with bath (with overhead shower).</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Queen Rooms</strong> are located on floors 7-14. These rooms are around 20m², sleep two people, and have an ensuite with shower. These rooms are available for single occupancy.</p>
<p><strong>Premium Single Rooms</strong> are around 19m² and on floors 7-11. They have an ensuite with shower. </p>
<p><strong>Two Room Suites</strong> are on the top floor (floor 15), are around 50m², and sleep two to four people (two rooms with an interconnecting door). An excellent option for families,  suites consist of two rooms with interconnecting door - one bedroom and one living area with double sofa bed. They have a corner bath and a separate shower. These rooms are available on request - please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p>Kettles and cups are available from reception for a refundable deposit of approx. CHF20 per kettle.</p>
<p><strong>General Information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. CHF3.50 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged 15 years and under are exempt</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
